package.json
> first file of application
> entry point to application
> meta data 
> packages
> build/start/test

>>>>>>>>Step to make package.json<<<<<<<<
** NodeJS in should be install
> go to cmd/terminal
> navigate to folder
> npm init
> answer all questions
> type yes

>>>>>>>>Step to install any package<<<<<<<<
** NodeJs must be installed
> go to cmd/terminal
> navigate to folder where you want to install
> npm i package name

npm i 

>>>>>>>>Step to generate React App<<<<<<<<
#window
......One Time For One System..........
> Run cmd as admin
> npm i -g create-react-app

......Next All Time in above System..........
> go to folder where you want app 
> create-react-app appname

###################---------#################

#mac/linux
......One Time For One System..........
> Open terminal
> sudo npm i -g create-react-app

......Next All Time in above System..........
> go to folder where you want app 
> create-react-app appname

>>>>>>>>Step to Run App<<<<<<<<
> open cmd/ terminal
> go inside app
> npm start
> http://localhost:3000


